<paragraph pageId="131" pageNumber="132">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph lastPageId="132" lastPageNumber="133" pageId="131" pageNumber="132">
This species is restricted to the Great Smoky Mountains National Park and adjacent mountain ranges in the southern Appalachians [see Kavanaugh 1979a: 
<pageBreakToken pageId="132" pageNumber="133" start="start">Fig</pageBreakToken>
